!define MUI_ABORTWARNING
!define MUI_WELCOMEPAGE_TITLE "Install Zen Canvas / 安装 Zen Canvas"
!define MUI_WELCOMEPAGE_TEXT "Zen Canvas is a local-first personal file lifecycle assistant.$\r$\n$\r$\nIt helps scan, search, preview, and organize files. Real move or rename operations require your confirmation before execution.$\r$\n$\r$\nZen Canvas does not upload your files by default."
